translations: 有魅力的；诱人的（dishy 的变形）

sentences.sentence: Rounding out the top 5 in the dishiest dad competition after Beckham and Pitt was celebrity chef Jamie Oliver.
sentences.translation: 排在贝克汉姆和皮特之后的第五名是名厨师杰米·奥利弗。

sentences.sentence: Rounding out the top 5 in the dishiest dad competition after Beckham and Pitt was celebrity chef Jamie Oliver, TV star Jonathan Ross and recent father Tom Cruise.
sentences.translation: 在“美味老爸”前5名得主中，紧随贝克汉姆和皮特之后的是明星厨师贾米·奥利弗、电视剧明星乔纳森·罗斯和身为人父的汤姆·克鲁斯。
